headline: Cboe to Launch Cash-Settled Bitcoin ETF Options as Crypto Booms
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Cboe Global Markets Inc. said it is set to list the first cash-settled index options related to the spot price of Bitcoin, marking the latest addition of cryptocurrency-related securities to traditional exchanges.
